        .row(style='width: 80%; margin: 20px auto 50px auto;')
            .col-sm(style='background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 3px;margin-right: 5px;')
                button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button' style='background: #004486; margin-bottom: 10px;') SUBSCRIBE
                p Do not miss investment opportunities. Be alerted via email a day before listed security token offerings are opened for investing.
            .col-sm(style='background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 3px;margin-left: 6px;')
                a.btn.btn-secondary(href="/profile/ico/create" type='button' style='background: #004486; margin-bottom: 10px;') LIST YOUR ICO
                p ICO listings are fact based. We do not promote or advertise investment deals unless explicitly mentioned.
